{"tid":1763083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"關於黨鐵附例狗","createTime":"2019-11-30T05:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T04:36:21.000Z","uid":5737,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3e539ba016a5d22a2e10c3529d5e86b549cbdc8e","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"基本上有一班老是常出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUWggNZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUWggNZ.png&h=81b46b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjAAxmu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjAAxmu.png&h=7bed5356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到上個post 咁多人問 見到佢地點算<br />\n其實完全唔撚洗驚佢地<br />\n佢地話就話捉鳩人跳閘推閘<br />\n好多人都淆哂 驚佢掂你捉你<br />\n其實分分鐘佢仲驚你反抗<br />\n問心邊個想搵工會無啦啦想流血？<br />\n有d都係鳩下鳩下咁就一日<br />\n但有d的確係退休既狗做<br />\n但當個個都唔撚驚呢班社會垃圾<br />\n跳閘推閘跳到佢懷疑人生<br />\n做咩要哂力捉鳩人跳閘就得<br />\n到時黨鐵就會cut cost 請呢班on9看閘<br />\n講一講佢地佈防<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb25414108d8a2bdf1c80aa0159b4b9582a3a38","tid":1763083,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2973232763987b184e01e2572bcd4f7413f8ecf2","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:07:05.000Z","msg":"大家要互相幫助先贏到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b672cf3f987506fa7729793841d041b1bead4365","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"當日我單機6個都走到<br />\n如果有手足幫手頂一兩個<br />\n更加佢地捉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1026a870110a6b8a67c7340175a4bdc47b6ac745","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d14fa742cc148bf5782020c25559fbe889588e1f","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"688dce0e5bef822568182e79af725166f2756ff8","tid":1763083,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14248b62ee5d926a2b3a090f1f6aa2f2460a7c6a","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"講多聲<br />\n如果佢地多數都係退休狗做<br />\n下次黨鐵見到佢地<br />\n記住唔好打到佢地殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f18a9f2b4ff097b0725df52f16ff654167e94f","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b68d24e1b21e3e6c8d9b4b4286cc20cb9af03ac","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3c66332a9ac6a5f5d955f9046fd56502c7b5464","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"係時候做攻果個 唔好做守"},{"pid":"96d028f8a705ae33c85dfc019e57cfa2219b585e","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6629170bc75e4c8e01d0801d6615f86b5ebc3c7b","tid":1763083,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"但你地做廢老卡都可以照用<br />\n但我唔覺得佢地係執法人員<br />\n只係一班社會垃圾<br />\n無咩要